\begin_layout Quotation
Note:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote
After completing the process of borrowing (Loans) and reservations (Reserve)
 do not forget to click Finish Transaction.
 Without pressing the Finish Transaction, all of the transactions will not
 be recorded into the system.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote
Starting with Senayan3-stable13 a feature is available to print a transaction
 note .
 To enable this feature, one must first enable the module in System Setup.
 See the documentation of the System.
 The Print command will appear after clicking Finish Transaction.
\end_layout

