\begin_layout Quote
Commencing with Senayan3-stable11, it is possible to determine the date
 of loan and return manually.
 That is, the date of loan and return can be determined without being based
 on the configuration in Loan Rules.
 For activation please see the Module System Configurations.
\end_layout

