Overdued List
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 Menu
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote
A facility to find members with overdue status.
 Information displayed in this facility is Member ID, Member Name, Title,
 Days overdue, Loan Date, Due Date.
 With this menu we can also do printing and search overdues.
 Overdues seraches are done by Member ID/Member Name, Loan Date From, Loan
 Date Until.
\end_layout

